description:
**DubaiPeeps** is the first **Dubai Community NFT Collection** that was handcrafted (not generated) as an homage to the people of Dubai. The collection holds a total of only **600 Single Edition NFTs**.
**All of our characters are fictional and do not relate to, or represent an individual or entity.*

**Utility for our exclusive holders:**

- **Recipe mint for a 3D Peep as per the peep you hold OR free mint of a generated 3d Peep (only gas fees apply).**

- **Mint all future projects at zero cost (only gas fees apply).**

- **Passive income through royalties (3% of each project for our DubaiPeeps holders) from all future projects as per the DubaiPeeps you hold, categorized through rarity.**

- **Access to customized Merch in real life and digital.**

- **Exclusive access to our real life “Holders Only” events.**

- **Own 10 or more DubaiPeeps to receive an airdrop of an AnonymousPeeps Genesis.** https://opensea.io/collection/anonymouspeeps-genesis
